general.gigTitle: develop a top notch website with expert web development

sellerCard.oneLiner: An award winning web development team in UK and UAE!
sellerCard.description: We provide an economical and user-friendly platform for all, enabling individuals and businesses to create and manage their websites effortlessly. We built our own CMS providing corporate websites, e-commerce web store and mobile app in a record TAT and budget!

description.content:
Grow your business with expert website development services!


Hello! We are providing expert website development services and designing services. We have worked with over 100+ clients around the globe and have achieved 98% customer satisfaction.


We can make all kinds of sites, whether it's eCommerce, listing, blogs, booking sites, hotels, community or real estate sites or any SaaS product.


Top reasons to work with us:


  • Expert website development, designing, and marketing consultants
  • 12+ years of experience
  • Worked with many startups and businesses
  • Prefer long-term clients and value-oriented services
  • Technical SEO experts


What our customers will receive:


  • Stunning and fully functional professional services
  • Highly responsive websites that runs smoothly on all devices
  • A site that loads within seconds
  • A site focused on user experience
  • SEO optimized websites
  • Cross-browser compatible
  • Professional and unique designs

 

Feel free to contact us if you have any questions. If you purchase the gig directly, fixed features will be delivered as per the gig and the package is to be renewed next year.

seller_response.comment: The project's timeline was 14 days but the client kept on insisting to deliver earlier. We needed to do frontend and integrate google map's API but client refused to provide the API even when it was mentioned before order placement. He kept on asking us to use our own bank details and provide it to him which is never possible for a freelancer. I purchased a theme out of my pocket and completed the first milestone of frontend. He still cancelled the order through customer support and now I am down $400 and I am not given a chance to explain my side of things to fiverr.
